rows.label: campfev11_550_190_msg0001
rows.name:
We've pretty much cleared the Gargoyles
out of the residential
and shopping districts, right?

rows.label: campfev11_550_190_msg0003
rows.name:
But it looks like they're gathering
in the courtyard now.

rows.label: campfev11_550_190_msg0004
rows.name: No time to rest, I guess...

rows.label: campfev11_550_190_msg0005
rows.name:
We'll just have to push on
a little longer.
